<varlistentry id="options.EatFocusClick">
	<term>EatFocusClick</term>
	<listitem>
	<para>When this flag is specified in feel file - AfterStep will "eat" mouse
        click, that was used to focus window in ClickToFocus mode. That means that
        if you have any function assigned to mouse clicks on the titlebars -
        those functions will only be executed if the window is already focused.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
